{"tid":800270,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"作為一個魚拉突 咁既分組真係得啖笑","createTime":"2018-08-30T17:07:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T17:21:33.000Z","uid":31314,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0b1d20870fbdc98547487d0b698166f1f4730cfd","tid":800270,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:07:14.000Z","msg":"講真咁同直接宣佈曼首名有咩分別。<br />\n<br />\n令我地班魚拉突 totally no mood to 捱夜睇波 嗱,我又分析下 首先祖雲達斯,唔好玩啦 意假野，6分穩陣<br />\n <br />\n華倫西亞,,如果係巴狗就有可觀性(順便可以報上次ga仇)(不過算啦,入到決賽又會見到面) 我真係冇睇過依隊野..曼半力夠WIN,又6分<br />\n<br />\n最後一隊,我連名都唔記得 我地出青年軍練下is ok,又6分<br />\n<br />\n加上我地4大尖刀 盧卡古,拉舒碌柒,馬迪爾,連加特 加上關鍵王普巴.. 根本場場大炒,,,,<br />\n<br />\n18分就一定..係睇下破唔破到得失球.咁一面倒ga比賽,我冇興趣,大家16強見<br />\n<br />\nP.S.比d咁ga對手魚拉突..is侮辱..哈"},{"pid":"c9c69aa2bcc3cb6f4dcc065f8300e44f478aeb8b","tid":800270,"uid":86756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:09:54.000Z","msg":"丙朗冇面見魚拉突"},{"pid":"20a58f1640b900ba883c56316404f5e71644fc5b","tid":800270,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:12:36.000Z","msg":"每年都用得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7800cc0898af1a6acb98ca4bb58acfd28fc4f5c","tid":800270,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20a58f1640b900ba883c56316404f5e71644fc5b","tid":800270,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:12:36.000Z","msg":"每年都用得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:16:30.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"191110055ce5c4a5da619a35f6ad42413b4840c4","tid":800270,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T17:18:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/04/223206_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018